ill warns about. · h3:Phase Fingerprint Scan=Scan against `assets/ai-tells-catalog.md`. Judge **clusters, single hits** one stray transition word human; inflated-significance phrasing plus forced triplet plus fake-depth "-ing" tails generated. Report scan (buzzword count, rhythm uniformity, hedging density, opinion presence) operator sees what's fixed. · h3:Phase 5-Pass Rewrite=protocol above. two non-negotiables sources: **rewrite tells around concrete claim underneath never delete trigger word leave stump**; injected pattern comes **from loaded voice**, generic "human-sounding" repertoire. Facts, numbers, qualifiers preserved exactly voice-matched claim became false worse failure robotic true one. · h3:Phase Cut Ladder=Top-down: kill whole sections/sentences takeaway doesn't need cut restatements (intros preview, closers recap) drop what context carries shorter words strip scaffolding ("it's important note that"). **The over-trimming guardrail applies**: qualifiers keep claims true, concrete specifics, personality (asides, opinions, varied rhythm) *last* things cut, first. floor meaning, word count. · h3:Phase Restore, Read Aloud, Ship=Read full text aloud voice's cadence; rewrite any sentence brand never say, scratch, voice. Verify restore check. output. · of=`## Rewritten ([brand] voice, guide [version] [+ archetype if used]) \· [the text] \·  \· ### What changed \· Vocabulary: [key swaps] \· Rhythm: [what broke the uniformity] \· Voice markers injected: [which]` · of=Quick mode batches: rewritten text one footer line. · pr=**Specific voice nothing.** "Sounds human" commodity; "sounds like brand" craft. fake imperfections, ever authenticity, deception., **Rewrite tells, don't strike them.** deleted buzzword still-generated sentence fixes nothing., **Clusters convict, single tells don't.**, **Cut whole units before trimming words.**, **Specifics true qualifiers survive pass.** LLMs round detail off; don't finish job., **The read-aloud test final judge.** sentence